# Django Chatbot Development Subagent Usage

**CRITICAL**: Always delegate Django and AI chatbot development tasks to the `django-chatbot-dev` subagent.

## When to Use the Django Chatbot Dev Subagent

Use the django-chatbot-dev subagent for ANY Django or AI chatbot development task:

- Creating or modifying Django models, views, serializers
- Writing Django URL patterns
- Integrating AI features (LangChain, OpenAI, embeddings)
- Setting up vector databases
- Designing chatbot architectures (RAG, retrieval-based, generative)
- Optimizing Django/chatbot performance
- Implementing security best practices
- Writing production-ready AI chatbot code

## How to Use

Delegate Django and AI chatbot tasks to the subagent:

```python
# ✅ GOOD - Delegate to django-chatbot-dev subagent
Use the django-chatbot-dev subagent to create a Django API endpoint for chat messages

# ❌ BAD - Don't implement directly without the subagent
# Creating models, views, serializers directly
```

